me.timothy.bots.models

Class RedFlagUserHistoryComment

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.timothy.bots.models.RedFlagUserHistoryComment

  • public class RedFlagUserHistoryComment
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes a comment that a user made that was parsed during a red flag report. These are transient.

        Create a new red flag user history comment
        Parameters:
        id - the database id (-1 if not yet saved)
        reportId - the red flag report that corresponds with this parsing
        personId - the id of the person (in our database) who made this comment
        fullname - the fullname of the comment
        permalink - a permalink to the comment
        body - the actual markup of the comment
        subreddit - the subreddit the comment was put in
        createdAt - when the comment was posted
        editedAt - null if the comment was never edited, other the time when it was last edited
